        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Jonathan_Favre\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"299510\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/jonathan_favre/48/1183_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Jonathan_Favre:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Andrew - don\u2019t forget to post on the '14 DRC Ech also!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>It was good, in a nice, soft place. Nose was bursting from the glass reminiscent of LT, but the palate was softer, less fruit and less vibrant. Fun to drink though!</p>",
